title: Reason2
---
Bug: You know . . . I just really want to see what this tree has to offer.
Squirrel: I still don't believe you. A little bug like you would never try to scale the tree, not with the birds always prowling around!
Bug: Okay . . . you're right. I'm actually trying to prove my innocence to the birds.
<<jump Reason1>>
